dc_title_s: West Indies, Cuba--south coast, Golfo de Batabanó, Cabo Francés to Punta las Cayamas, including Isla de la Juventud (Isla de Pinos) (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From Cuban charts to 1976." "Copyright 1995 by the United States government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Map NO.27141 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
